title: Does expat life really make you healthier, wealthier and happier?
text: Expat Health Does expat life really make you healthier, wealthier and happier? With a new survey suggesting that moving overseas is the answer to nearly all your problems, we asked those who’ve done it whether that’s true ... Is life abroad as good as they say it is? Photo: Alamy
